snippet: Laura Diaz, without a title in the past 12 years on the L.P.G.A. Tour, shot a nine-under-par 62 for a four-stroke lead after the opening round of the Marathon Classic in Sylvania, Ohio.
abstract: Laura Diaz takes first-round lead at the Marathon Classic LPGA golf tournament in Sylvania, Ohio.
lead_paragraph: Laura Diaz, without a title in the past 12 years on the L.P.G.A. Tour, shot a nine-under-par 62 for a four-stroke lead after the opening round of the Marathon Classic in Sylvania, Ohio.
